name: Save Survicate survey results in Google Sheets
description: Every time a Survicate survey is completed, Make will automatically save the results in Google Sheets. This template uses the "User Experience Survey" model from Survicate and [this example spreadsheet](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1NSElzYeSS007jhjA3L4p_l3-Hiv5BrEsrwnd0cejIhg/edit?usp=sharing).
